28. Abbreviated Texts on Training Rules
293. An Ājīvaka
“Mendicants, an <i>Ājīvaka</i> ascetic with five qualities is cast down to hell.
What five?
They kill living creatures, steal, have sex, lie, and use alcoholic drinks that cause negligence.
An <i>Ājīvaka</i> ascetic with these five qualities is cast down to hell.”

